Description:
    The activity_streams generator generates controllers and tests for the activity_streams plug-in.  

Example:
    ./script/generate activity_streams User

    This will create:
        db/migrate/xxxxx_create_actiivty_streams.rb
        config/initializers/activity_streams.rb
        app/controllers/activity_stream_controller.rb
        app/controllers/activity_stream_preferencescontroller.rb
        test/functional/activity_stream_preferences_controller_test.rb
        test/functional/activity_streams_controller_test.rb
        test/integration/activity_stream_preferences_integration_test.rb
        test/unit/activity_stream_test.rb
        test/fixtures/activity_streams.yml
